Vertical Option Spreads, Website: A Study of the 1.8 Standard Deviation Inflection Point


2013 | ISBN: 1118537009 | English | 256 Pages | EPUB | 3.05 MB

Make trades on vertical options spreads with the precision of a laser beam

Vertical Options Spreads is a combination of a bona-fide academic research-based study and a complete method to trade credit and debit spreads, along with other complex option combination trades such as iron condors and butterflies.
